chunk #566 , size:43
BIOGRAPHY  Jennifer Douglas is an associate
-----
chunk #567 , size:39
professor at the School of Information,
-----
chunk #568 , size:38
University of British Columbia, on the
-----
chunk #569 , size:48
traditional, ancestral, and unceded territory of
-----
chunk #570 , size:47
the xʷməθkʷəy̓əm (Musqueam) First Nation, where
-----
chunk #571 , size:47
she teaches courses on archival arrangement and
-----
chunk #572 , size:49
description, personal and community archives, and
-----
chunk #573 , size:47
research methodologies. Her research is focused
-----
chunk #574 , size:46
